title: Udemy the Best Year of Your Life Coach Yourself to Success Tutor
description:
Udemy the Best Year of Your Life Coach Yourself to Success Tutorial


What are the requirements?

- You must be ready to change the way you do things currently.
- Motivation to DO and not to just watch.

What am I going to get from this course?

- Over 6 lectures and 42 mins of content!
- Learn to use the method professional coaches use with their clients on yourself
- Achieve things they never thought possible and get real, tangible results
- Get an effective tool to use in problem solving to overcome what's holding them back.
- Gain skills, knowledge and confidence to improve performance and confidence.

What is the target audience?

- Small to Medium business owners
- Entreprenuers
- Anyone looking to increase personal or work effectiveness
